<!DOCTYPE qhelp SYSTEM "qhelp.dtd">
<qhelp>
  <overview>
    <p>HTML and dynamic-code APIs can interpret strings as markup or JavaScript.</p>
  </overview>
  <recommendation>
    <p>Avoid these APIs. If one is required, use a reviewed sanitizer and document the reason at the call site.</p>
  </recommendation>
</qhelp>
